[HEADER]
id: guardian_dead
title: Guardian Defeated

[CONTENT]
The guardian cracks, then collapses into still stone.
Inside the chest, beneath the coins, lies a heavy iron key carved with the same skull mark as the dungeon door.
When you touch it, distant locks seem to click in the dark.

